Exercise 3

qiime2
## phyloseq-class experiment-level object
## otu_table()   OTU Table:         [ 2351 taxa and 7 samples ]
## sample_data() Sample Data:       [ 7 samples by 22 sample variables ]
## tax_table()   Taxonomy Table:    [ 2351 taxa by 7 taxonomic ranks ]
physeq_percent = transform_sample_counts(qiime2, function(x) 100 * x/sum(x))
plot_bar(physeq_percent, fill="Genus") + 
  geom_bar(aes(fill=Genus), stat="identity") +
  labs( x = "Sample Depth(m)", y = "Abundance (%)", title = "Phylum Abundance Through Saanich Inlet Depth") +
  theme(legend.position="right")
